BrainFile-class          package:NeuroImage          R Documentation

"_B_r_a_i_n_F_i_l_e" _v_i_r_t_u_a_l _c_l_a_s_s

_D_e_s_c_r_i_p_t_i_o_n:

     A class that encapsulates function associated with brain image
     input/output

_O_b_j_e_c_t_s _f_r_o_m _t_h_e _C_l_a_s_s:

     A virtual Class: No objects may be created from it.

_S_l_o_t_s:


     '_p_a_t_h': Object of class '"character"' : the path to the image file             

     '_o_p_e_n': Object of class '"character"' : whether the file to be
          opened for read "r" or write  "w" 


_M_e_t_h_o_d_s:


     _o_p_e_n_F_o_r 'signature(x = "BrainFile")': querues whether file is open
          for read or write 

     _p_a_t_h 'signature(x = "BrainFile")': the full path of the file  

     _s_h_o_w 'signature(x = "BrainFile")': print a text representation of
          the 'BrainFile' object 

     _f_i_l_e_N_a_m_e 'signature(x = "BrainFile")': return the file name of the
          current connection 

     _f_i_l_e_T_y_p_e 'signature(x = "BrainFile")': return the file type of the
          backing file (e.g. NIFTI) 


